    public abstract class EditableAction<I extends Editable,O>
extends WindowAction<O>
    An EditableAction is an action applicable to some non-null editable objects. Before the main process of this action, it checks if it is applicable to the active object in #preProcess(ProgressDialog).
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
    See Also:
